<subSubSection id="B5F66544FFFDCA79FA51F6832755F646" pageId="3" pageNumber="46" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="FD5336CFFFFDCA79FA51F6832755F646" blockId="3.[1443,2650,1794,2538]" pageId="3" pageNumber="46">
<emphasis id="CF98EADDFFFDCA79FA51F6832832F697" bold="true" box="[1445,1794,2346,2379]" pageId="3" pageNumber="46">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List (as D. yepest). Additional research is required to understand natural history and conservation status of the Yungas Lesser Long-nosed Armadillo.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
